      <title>尼日利亚提出新的税收优惠政策吸引天然气投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nigeria-proposes-new-tax-incentives-to-attract-gas-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位政府官员表示，尼日利亚希望通过新的深水天然气勘探政策框架中提出的税收减免和其他措施，吸引高达 100 亿美元的新投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nigeria-proposes-new-tax-incentives-to-attract-gas-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:57:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥 Sheinbaum 计划未来几年将最低工资提高 12%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-plans-12-minimum-wage-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆表示，她计划在 2025 年及随后几年将最低工资提高约 12%，这一增幅将远高于拉丁美洲第二大经济体的通货膨胀率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mexico-s-sheinbaum-plans-12-minimum-wage-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:34:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登言论导致油价飙升，以色列袭击真主党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/israel-strikes-hezbollah-as-biden-comments-send-oil-surging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列继续推进对真主党武装分子的军事行动，在黎巴嫩南部发动冲突并对贝鲁特实施空袭，而美国及其盟友则准备应对以色列对伊朗本周早些时候发射弹道导弹进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/israel-strikes-hezbollah-as-biden-comments-send-oil-surging</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国关闭与俄罗斯情报人员有关的黑客使用的网站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/us-takes-down-websites-used-by-hackers-linked-to-fsb-doj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国司法部和微软公司称，美国政府和微软公司已查获了俄罗斯情报人员及其在美国的代理人使用的 107 个网站。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/us-takes-down-websites-used-by-hackers-linked-to-fsb-doj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥移民被杀案促使 Sheinbaum 誓言展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mexico-s-military-kills-migrants-leading-sheinbaum-to-vow-to-investigate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆承诺调查军方枪击一辆载有移民的卡车并导致六人死亡的事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mexico-s-military-kills-migrants-leading-sheinbaum-to-vow-to-investigate</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 15:49:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗实力减弱引发担忧，可能推动发展核武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/weakened-iran-raises-fears-it-may-make-push-for-nuclear-weapons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周以来，以色列不断袭击，伊朗的代理人真主党和哈马斯势力被削弱，伊朗很少像现在这样处于被动地位。而德黑兰周二向以色列发射了约 200 枚导弹，美国认为这些导弹“无效”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/weakened-iran-raises-fears-it-may-make-push-for-nuclear-weapons</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 14:59:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洪水和经济疲软导致奥地利 2024 年无法实现欧盟预算目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/austria-to-miss-eu-budget-goal-in-2024-on-floods-weak-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利表示，更严重的经济下滑和近期洪水造成的支出很可能使其预算赤字超过欧盟的限额，这加大了联邦选举后紧缩政策的紧迫性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/austria-to-miss-eu-budget-goal-in-2024-on-floods-weak-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 14:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯确认其军队已控制乌克兰乌赫莱达尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/russia-confirms-its-forces-took-control-of-ukraine-s-vuhledar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国防部正式确认，俄罗斯军队已夺取顿涅茨克地区具有重要战略意义的煤矿城镇武赫莱达尔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/russia-confirms-its-forces-took-control-of-ukraine-s-vuhledar</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 14:35:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦称俄罗斯投入巨资阻挠其加入欧盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/moldova-says-russia-channeling-millions-to-thwart-its-eu-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦当局称，他们发现了一项由俄罗斯支持的行动，涉及 13 万名摩尔多瓦公民，旨在影响本月对总统玛雅·桑杜的欧洲愿望至关重要的投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/moldova-says-russia-channeling-millions-to-thwart-its-eu-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 12:49:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将查戈斯群岛割让给毛里求斯，保留对迭戈加西亚军事基地的控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mauritius-government-agrees-deal-with-uk-on-chagos-archipelago</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国与毛里求斯达成协议，允许其在未来一个世纪继续控制印度洋上具有重要战略意义的英美军事基地，同时将查戈斯群岛的主权割让给毛里求斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mauritius-government-agrees-deal-with-uk-on-chagos-archipelago</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 10:11:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
